data.title: Famous birthdays list for today, March 26, 2024 includes celebrities Keira Knightley, Kenny Chesney
data.meta_description: Keira Knightley and Kenny Chesney share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of celebrities and other famous people with birthdays on March 26, 2024 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Keira Knightley, Kenny Chesney and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on March 26th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on March 26, 2024

Singer Diana Ross turns 80

Fun fact: Singer and actress Ashlee Simpson is her daughter-in-law

Rocker Steven Tyler turns 76

Fun fact: Voiced The Mad Hatter in an episode of ‘Wonder Pets’

TV personality Vicki Lawrence turns 75

Fun fact: Her son once appeared as an extra in an episode of ‘Mama’s Family’

Comedian Martin Short turns 74

Fun fact: Had a small cameo in the ‘Aquaman’ sequel as a villain

Check out other celebrities born in Canada >>>

Actress Jennifer Grey turns 64

Fun fact: Was once a contestant on ‘Dancing with the Stars’

Actor Michael Imperioli turns 58

Fun fact: Was once engaged to actress Lili Taylor

Country singer Kenny Chesney turns 56

Fun fact: Originally from Knoxville, TN

Actress Leslie Mann turns 52

Fun fact: Appeared as a nurse early in her career on a show called ‘Birdland’

Actress Amy Smart turns 48

Fun fact: Played the mother of ‘Stargirl’ on the CW series

Actress Keira Knightley turns 39

Fun fact: Has twice been nominated for Oscars

Actress Carly Chaikin turns 34

Fun fact: Her middle name is Hannah

More celebrities with birthdays today

Actor Ernest Thomas (“Everybody Hates Chris,” ″What’s Happening”) is 75. Country singer Ronnie McDowell is 74. Drummer Monte Yoho of The Outlaws is 72. Country singer Dean Dillon is 69. Country singer Charly McClain is 68. Talk show host Leeza Gibbons is 67. Actor Ellia English (“The Jamie Foxx Show,” ″Curb Your Enthusiasm”) is 65. Actor Billy Warlock (“Baywatch”) is 63. Actor Eric Allan Kramer (“The Hughleys”) is 62. Guitarist James Iha of Smashing Pumpkins is 56. Actor T.R. Knight (“Grey’s Anatomy”) is 51. Rapper Juvenile is 49. Actor Bianca Kajlich (“Rules of Engagement,” ″Boston Public”) is 47. “Face the Nation” moderator Margaret Brennan is 44. Rapper J-Kwon is 38.
